<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>PEZ Voter Thingee</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#800000" vlink="#800000" alink="#FFFFFF">
  <p></p>
  <ol>
    <li>Please <b>FIRST</b> check the selection list next to the category you are voting for to be sure your dispenser isn't already in the database. If it is, just select it, and click on VOTE. Be sure to leave the text blank empty.</li>
    <li>If your dispenser is <b>NOT</b> in the selection list, you may type it into the empty blank. Click on VOTE. Anything typed in the blank will override the selection list.</li>
  </ol>
  <hr noshade>
  <a href="/cgi-bin/vote.cgi?m=show">View the Voting Results</a>
  <p></p>
  <center>
    <table border="0" width="95%" cellpadding="3">
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#EDBA7D">
          <b>Favorite CURRENT Dispenser</b>
          <p></p>
          <form method="post" action="http://pezheads.org/cgi-bin/vote.cgi">
            <input type="hidden" value="display" name="m"><input type="hidden" name="section" value="Favorite Current"><select name="url">
            </select> or<br>
            <input type="text" name="url2" maxlength="30" size="30"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="VOTE">
          </form>
        </td>
        <td rowspan="3" width="2" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"></td>
        <td bgcolor="#EDBA7D">
          <b>Do You EAT the PEZ Candy?</b>
          <p></p>
          <form method="post" action="http://pezheads.org/cgi-bin/vote.cgi">
            <input type="hidden" value="display" name="m"><input type="hidden" name="section" value="Eat"> <select name="url">
            </select> or<br>
            <input type="text" name="url2" maxlength="30" size="30"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="VOTE">
          </form>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="2" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"></td>
        <td height="2" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#EDBA7D">
          <b>You've Been Collecting Since</b>
          <p></p>
          <form method="post" action="http://pezheads.org/cgi-bin/vote.cgi">
            <input type="hidden" value="display" name="m"><input type="hidden" name="section" value="Collecting Since"> <select name="url">
            </select> or<br>
            <input type="text" maxlength="30" name="url2" size="30"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="VOTE">
          </form>
        </td>
        <td bgcolor="#EDBA7D">
          <b>What Flavor Should They Make Next?</b>
          <p></p>
          <form method="post" action="http://pezheads.org/cgi-bin/vote.cgi">
            <input type="hidden" value="display" name="m"><input type="hidden" name="section" value="Flavor"> <select name="url">
            </select> or<br>
            <input type="text" maxlength="30" name="url2" size="30"><br>
            <input type="submit" value="VOTE">
          </form>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </center>
  <p><a href="/index.html"></a> <a href="/cgi-bin/vote.cgi?m=show">View the Voting Results</a></p>
  <p><br clear="all"></p>
  <hr size="6" width="75%">
